[{"Id": 1010839, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "In his book of al-Misbah, Shaykh Tusi has reported Safwan as saying from Imam Sadiq (a) that before you proceed for journey, keep 3 fasts and on the 3rd day perform ghusl, wear pure (paak) clothes, apply perfume, gather your family members, offer a 2 rakat Namaz (like Namaz-e-Fajr), pray for safe journey, recite <Aayatul Kursi>, praise Allah (swt), invoke salawaat and recite dua <Allahumma inni astawde okal>.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Shaikh Tusi ne apni kitaab Misbah mein Imam Sadiq (a) se riwaayat ki hai keh Imam (a) ne farmaaya keh safar pe jaane se pehle 3 din roza rakkhe aur thisre din (3rd day) ghusl kare, paak o saaf libaas pehne, khusboo lagaaye, apne khaandaan waalo’n ko jama kare, namaz-e-subh ki tarah 2 rakat namaz adaa kare aur phir Allah se apni khairiyat ki dua maange, <Aayatul Kursi> padhe, Allah (swt) ki hamd o sana baja laaye, salawaat padhe aur phir dua <Allahumma inni astawde okal> padhe.", "UrduDescription": "سفر پر جانے سے قبل ۳ دن روزہ رکھے اور تیسرے دن غسل کرے، غسل کے بعدپھر اپنے اہل وعیال کو جمع کرکے ۲ رکعت نماز ادا کرے اور حق تعالیٰ سے اپنی خیریت کی دعا مانگے اور اس کے بعد<آیت الکرسی> پڑھے، اﷲ کی حمد و ثنا بجا لائے، محمدؐ وآل محمد ؑپر درود بھیجے اور پھر دعا <اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَسْتَوْدِعُكَ> پڑھے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010848, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "You may then bid your family members farewell and stand up. At the door of your house, you may recite Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s), <Surah Fateha> and <Aayatul Kursi> in front of you, on your right side, and on your left side. You may then recite dua <Allahumma ilaika wajjahto>.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ab apne ahel o ayaal ko wida kare aur apne makaan ke darwaaze par khade ho kar Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s) padhe, phir <Surah Fateha> aur <Aayatul Kursi> apne saamne (front), daayne (right) aur baaye’n (left) teeno taraf padhe. Phir dua <Allahumma ilaika wajjahto> padhe.", "UrduDescription": "اس کے بعد اپنے اہل وعیال کو وداع کرے اور اپنے مکان کے دروازے پر کھڑے ہوکر تسبیح فاطمہ زہرا ؑ پڑھے،پھر سامنے دائیں اور بائیں طرف منہ کر کے <سورۂ فاتحہ> پڑھے اور اسی طرح <آیت الکرسی> بھی تینوں طرف منہ کر کے ایک ایک مرتبہ پڑھے،پھر دعا <اَللّٰهُمَّ اِلَيْكَ وَجَّهْتُ> پڑھے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010849, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 3, "EnglishDescription": "You may then recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 11-times, <Surah Qadr>, <Aayatul Kursi>, <Surah Falaq>, and <Surah Naas> once, and then pass your hand over your entire body, give sadaqa (alms) as much as possible, and recite dua <Allahumma inni ish tarai-to>.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ab 11 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe, 1 martaba <Surah Qadr>, <Aayatul Kursi>, <Surah Falaq> aur <Surah Naas> padh kar apne haatho’n ko badan par phere aur jitna ho sakey sadaqa de aur phir dua <Allahumma inni ish tarai-to> padhe.", "UrduDescription": "پھر ۱۱ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> پڑھے،ایک مرتبہ <سورۂ قدر>، <آیت الکرسی>، <سورۂ فلق> اور <سورۂ ناس> پڑھ کر اپنے ہاتھوں کو بدن پر مس کرے اور جس قدر ہوسکے صدقہ دے اور پھر دعا <اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اِشْتَرَيْتُ> پڑھے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "Ara