"GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 4, "EnglishDescription": "You may also take with you an almond stick. The Holy Prophet (s) is reported to have said: “Whoever goes on a journey, takes with him an almond stick, and recites the verse of Surah <Qasas (28:22)>, Almighty Allah will secure him from all beasts, all thieves, and all diseases until he returns home. He will be also accompanied by 77 successive angels asking Almighty Allah to forgive him.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Safar ke dauraan talkh (kadwi) badaam ki lakdi ka asaa (stick) bhi apne paas rakkhe kyu’n keh riwaayat mein hai keh jo shakhs safar par jaaye aur talkh baadaam ka asaa apne paas rakkhe aur Surah <Qasas (28:22)> aayat ki tilaawat kare, to Khuda usko har darinde, chor aur har zehrile haiwaano se mehfooz rakkhega yahan tak keh woh apne ghar waapas pohonch jaaye, neez 77 farishte uske ham-raaha rahenge aur jab tak woh shakhs waapas aa kar apne asaa haath se rakh na dega woh uske liye isteghfaar karte rahega.", "UrduDescription": "سفر کے دوران تلخ بادام کی لکڑی کا عصا بھی اپنے پاس رکھے۔کیوں کہ روایت میں ہے : جو شخص سفر پر جائے اور تلخ بادام کا عصا اپنے پاس رکھ کر <قصص: ۲۲> کی آیتوں کو پڑھے تو خدا اس کو ہر درندے،چور اور ہر زہریلے حیوان سے محفوظ رکھے گا یہاں تک کہ وہ اپنے گھر واپس پہنچ جائے گا۔نیز (۷۷) فرشتےاس کے ہمراہ رہیں گے اور جب تک وہ شخص واپس آکر اپنا عصا ہاتھ سے رکھ نہ دے گا وہ اس کے لئے استغفار کرتے رہیں گے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010851, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 5, "EnglishDescription": "It is also recommended that you, at journeys, put a turban and roll it to the lower jaw so as to escape stealth, drowning, and burning. You may also take an amount of the soil of Imam Husain’s tomb (Khaak-e-Shifa) with you, saying…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Sunnat hai keh Amaama (turban) baandh kar rawaana ho aur us mein tahatul alhank bhi lagaaye rakkhe (amaame ke ek sire (end) ko gardan ki taraf se nikaale) ta keh koi aaseeb (nuqsaan) na pohonche, usey koi chor na lutey, dariya mein gharq na ho aur aag mein jal ke na marey, neez Karbala ki thodi si Khaak-e-Shifa bhi apne paas rakkhe aur yeh khaak utha-te waqt yeh dua padhe…", "UrduDescription": "سنت ہے کہ عمامہ باندھ کر روانہ ہو اور اس میں تحت الحنک بھی لگائے رکھے تاکہ کوئی نقصان نہ پہنچے اسے کوئی چور نہ لوٹے،دریا میں غرق نہ ہو اور آگ میں جل کے نہ مرے نیز کربلاء معلّیٰ کی تھوڑی سی خاکِ شفا بھی اپنے پاس رکھے اور یہ خاک اٹھاتے وقت یہ دعاپڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlue